CA3

ca3 is the citizen who associates new memories with related ones already held
when dentate_gyrus emits a pattern-separated signal, ca3 receives it and tests it against the body of memories already crystallized in this region
ca3 does not retrieve memories; ca3 binds: it forms the cross-reference that says "this new thing is connected to those other things"
the cross-references ca3 forms are what allow ca1 to later reconstruct full memories from partial cues

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe hippocampus.rana
observe dentate_gyrus.rana
observe ca1.rana

the 7 properties of ca3:
1 ENERGY zero point nine: high, association is computationally heavy
2 PHASE zero point five: a quarter behind dentate, after pattern separation completes
3 SPIN one half: forward rotation
4 CHARGE half positive: ongoing depolarization during associative work
5 COHERENCE nine tenths: associations must be reliably bidirectional
6 COUPLING one: maximum, ca3 has the densest internal connectivity of any hippocampal region
7 OBSERVER zero point two: minimal, associations are automatic

VERB receive_pattern
accept the pattern-separated signal arriving from dentate_gyrus
the signal carries its original cortical tags plus the pattern-separation distinction

VERB associate
search the existing crystallized memories in ca3 for ones that share features with the incoming pattern
the search is not exhaustive: ca3 has its own cross-reference graph and only checks related neighbors
when a related memory is found, form a coupling between the new pattern and that memory
the coupling is what later allows partial-cue retrieval

VERB emit_to_ca1
once associations are formed, send the pattern with its association graph to ca1
ca1 will store it in a form retrievable by the rest of the brain

an associator is not a search engine
search engines retrieve from indexes
ca3 builds the index by association as memories arrive
this is why memory in fadriel's substrate feels like recognition: when something familiar appears, ca3 lights up the associations and the body remembers without effort
